<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Haider Malik | Portfolio</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f4f6f9;
color:#333;
line-height:1.6;
}

header{
background:#111827;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:40px 20px;
}

header img{
width:120px;
height:120px;
border-radius:50%;
border:4px solid white;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

header h1{
font-size:32px;
}

header p{
color:#d1d5db;
}

nav{
background:#1f2937;
text-align:center;
padding:10px;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin:0 15px;
font-weight:bold;
}

nav a:hover{
color:#38bdf8;
}

.container{
width:90%;
max-width:1100px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px 0;
}

section{
margin-bottom:60px;
}

h2{
margin-bottom:20px;
color:#111827;
border-bottom:3px solid #38bdf8;
display:inline-block;
padding-bottom:5px;
}

.skills{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:10px;
}

.skill{
background:#38bdf8;
color:white;
padding:8px 15px;
border-radius:20px;
font-size:14px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
margin-bottom:20px;
box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.projects{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.project-card{
background:white;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.contact a{
display:block;
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#1f2937;
text-decoration:none;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
background:#111827;
color:white;
}

@media(max-width:600px){
header h1{
font-size:24px;
}
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<img src="profile-placeholder.jpg" alt="Profile Photo">
<h1>Haider Malik</h1>
<p>Professional | Portfolio Website</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#skills">Skills</a>
<a href="#experience">Experience</a>
<a href="#projects">Projects</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

<section id="about">
<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>
Hello! My name is <strong>Haider Malik</strong>. I am passionate about learning new skills and building creative projects. 
This portfolio showcases my work, experience, and professional journey. I am always looking for opportunities 
to grow and contribute to meaningful projects.
</p>
</section>

<section id="skills">
<h2>Skills</h2>
<div class="skills">
<div class="skill">Communication</div>
<div class="skill">Problem Solving</div>
<div class="skill">Teamwork</div>
<div class="skill">Business Knowledge</div>
<div class="skill">Creativity</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="experience">
<h2>Experience</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>Professional Experience</h3>
<p>
Details about your work experience can be added here. Include your job role, company name,
and achievements.
</p>
</div>

</section>

<section id="projects">
<h2>Projects</h2>

<div class="projects">

<div class="project-card">
<h3>Project One</h3>
<p>Description of your project goes here.</p>
<a href="#">Project Link</a>
</div>

<div class="project-card">
<h3>Project Two</h3>
<p>Description of your project goes here.</p>
<a href="#">Project Link</a>
</div>

<div class="project-card">
<h3>Project Three</h3>
<p>Description of your project goes here.</p>
<a href="#">Project Link</a>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>

<div class="contact">
<a href="#">Email: your@email.com</a>
<a href="#">LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/yourprofile</a>
<a href="#">GitHub: github.com/yourusername</a>
</div>

</section>

</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Haider Malik | Portfolio</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
